{"tid":2420932,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★1998年 香港調整股票印花稅後，恒指下跌44%！！！！","createTime":"2021-02-24T07:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T12:20:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2e807c3d6fcbbdc16330c6d82881c89af8ab0af8","tid":2420932,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:38:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>●歷來港調整股票印花稅後港股如何走？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，自1993年以來，香港股票印花稅曾作出調整，但曆次調整均為下調。其中，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>1998年4月調整後4個月，恒指下跌44%</strong></span>後觸底；2001年9月調整後4個月，恒指累計上升30%。以此觀之，今次港府建議增加股票印花稅，港股暫未有往績參考，股民只有自己計自己數，摸着石頭過河，見步行步！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210224/bkn-20210224133920437-0224_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210224%2Fbkn-20210224133920437-0224_00842_001.html&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7Tr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=dba542e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210224/bkn-20210224133920437-0224_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a77639a1770acb2ce40b4f88124349f8fe9fab66","tid":2420932,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71a23bd29c0e3b39e32bcd3fbf58fb7d20f5e6a","tid":2420932,"uid":21634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:38:56.000Z","msg":"酒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset